{"tid":1536121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為左呢場運動，我地仲有嘢可以做！！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:14:50.000Z","uid":317373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49a74da8e986244a272cb1b7969f06bd1d5476d2","tid":1536121,"uid":317373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"運動由六月開始到呢家，已經3個幾月，每日每星期都有手足送頭受傷，睇到又心痛又嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。每次行動高風險低回報，長遠唔係辦法 <br />\n係時候開拓更多嘅路出來行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">旁敲側擊！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路都唔係好多人aware，大家都記得麗晶單野<br />\n我地住緊嘅屋苑有樣野叫做大厦業主立案法團，大部分遍佈十八區嘅主席同委員都係藍絲，但係我地勝在人多有民意支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足可以叫下身邊嘅同路業主參選，趁住法團改選嚟個大洗牌，踢走獻世派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！<br />\n仲有從今日起，記住唔好簽授權書俾任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，自己的票自己投！！<br />\n<br />\n建議巴絲搵料起各區法團底，針對去做野，逐區改變，目標係直迫建制爪牙，削弱影響力，喺民居播種，到時就真係<strong>we connect</strong>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意！呢個係長期戰線持久戰，要ready好持續抗爭，各有各做，開更多戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣傳出去俾多d和理非業主知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">光復屋苑，時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4661e09bdb04f14b895ae6336e90dd376da93f70","tid":1536121,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a73e620b68eb056ac737aeee5a93ebe5a373fd11","tid":1536121,"uid":317373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a74da8e986244a272cb1b7969f06bd1d5476d2","tid":1536121,"uid":317373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"運動由六月開始到呢家，已經3個幾月，每日每星期都有手足送頭受傷，睇到又心痛又嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。每次行動高風險低回報，長遠唔係辦法 <br />\n係時候開拓更多嘅路出來行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">旁敲側擊！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路都唔係好多人aware，大家都記得麗晶單野<br />\n我地住緊嘅屋苑有樣野叫做大厦業主立案法團，大部分遍佈十八區嘅主席同委員都係藍絲，但係我地勝在人多有民意支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足可以叫下身邊嘅同路業主參選，趁住法團改選嚟個大洗牌，踢走獻世派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！<br />\n仲有從今日起，記住唔好簽授權書俾任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /